				"title": "Behandlingscheman vid insulinbehandling av typ 1-diabetes",
				"id": "",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"164\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"140\">\r\n<p><strong>Tillst&aring;nd</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"144\">\r\n<p><strong>Insulinsort</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"171\">\r\n<p><strong>Administrationsformer</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td rowspan=\"2\" width=\"164\">\r\n<p><strong>Vid debut</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"140\">\r\n<p>Ketoacidos</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"144\">\r\n<p>Snabbverkande humaninsulin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"171\">\r\n<p>Intraven&ouml;s infusion</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"140\">\r\n<p>Hyperglykemi utan ketoacidos</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"144\">\r\n<p>Snabbverkande insulinanalog (m&aring;ltidsinsulin) + basinsulin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"171\">\r\n<p>Multipla subkutana injektioner</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"164\">\r\n<p><strong>Underh&aring;llsbehandling</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"140\">\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Grundprincip vid typ 1-diabetes</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"144\">\r\n<p>Snabbverkande insulinanalog (m&aring;ltidsinsulin) + basinsulin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"171\">\r\n<p>Snabbverkande insulinanalog + insulin glargin 100 e/ml eller 300 E/ml, detemir eller degludek</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"164\">\r\n<p><strong>Tillf&auml;llig behandling</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"140\">\r\n<p>Hyperglykemi +/- ketonemi. Akuta tillst&aring;nd (feber, infektion, hj&auml;rtinfarkt)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"144\">\r\n<p>Snabbverkande insulinanalog (m&aring;ltidsinsulin) + basinsulin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"171\">\r\n<p>&Ouml;ka dosen vid ordinarie dostillf&auml;llen</p>\r\n<p>Intraven&ouml;s infusion vid behov</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>"
