				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"3\" width=\"655\">\r\n<p><strong>Basinsu</strong><strong>lin&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong><strong>Produk</strong><strong>t</strong><strong>n</strong><strong>am</strong><strong>n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong><strong>D</strong><strong>ur</strong><strong>at</strong><strong>ion</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"195\">\r\n<p>Humaninsulin NPH (medell&aring;ngverkande)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"241\">\r\n<p>Insuman Basal Humulin NPH Insulatard</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"218\">\r\n<p>12&ndash;18 timmar*</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"195\">\r\n<p>Insulin degludek (l&aring;ngverkande&nbsp; &nbsp;insulinanalog)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"241\">\r\n<p>Tresiba</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"218\">\r\n<p>&gt; 24 timmar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"195\">\r\n<p>Insulin detemir (l&aring;ngverkande&nbsp; &nbsp;insulinanalog)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"241\">\r\n<p>Levemir</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"218\">\r\n<p>12&ndash;20 timmar**</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"195\">\r\n<p>Insulin glargin 100 E/ml (l&aring;ngverkande&nbsp; &nbsp;insulinanalog)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"241\">\r\n<p>Lantus Abasaglar Lusduna</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"218\">\r\n<p>Upp till 24 timmar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"195\">\r\n<p>Insulin glargin 300 E/ml (l&aring;ngverkande&nbsp; &nbsp;insulinanalog)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"241\">\r\n<p>Toujeo</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"218\">\r\n<p>&gt; 24 timmar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"195\">\r\n<p><strong>Snabbv</strong><strong>erka</strong><strong>nd</strong><strong>e</strong> <strong>insulin</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" width=\"460\">\r\n<p><strong>D</strong><strong>ur</strong><strong>at</strong><strong>ion</strong><strong> (maxeffekt)</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"195\">\r\n<p>Humaninsulin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"241\">\r\n<p>Actrapid Humulin Regular Insuman Rapid</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"218\">\r\n<p>4&ndash;6 timmar (1,5&ndash;2,5 timmar)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"195\">\r\n<p><strong>M</strong><strong>&aring;l</strong><strong>t</strong><strong>idsinsulin</strong><strong>***</strong></p>\r\n<p>(snabbverkande insulinanalog)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"241\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"218\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"195\">\r\n<p>Insulin aspart</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"241\">\r\n<p>Fiasp#, NovoRapid</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"218\">\r\n<p>2&ndash;4 timmar (0,5&ndash;1,0 timmar)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"195\">\r\n<p>Insulin glulisin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"241\">\r\n<p>Apidra</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"218\">\r\n<p>2&ndash;4 timmar (0,5&ndash;1,0 timmar)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"195\">\r\n<p>Insulin lispro</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"241\">\r\n<p>Humalog</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"218\">\r\n<p>2&ndash;4 timmar (0,5&ndash;1,0 timmar)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>* Data baseras p&aring; tillg&auml;ngliga studier samt p&aring; konsensus i expertgruppen f&ouml;r &rdquo;Behandlingsrekommenationerna f&ouml;r l&auml;kemedelsbehandling f&ouml;r glukoskontroll vid typ-2 diabetes(2017)&rdquo; d&aring; det saknas direkta j&auml;mf&ouml;relser mellan alla olika typer av insuliner.</p>\r\n<p>** Enligt klinisk erfarenhet (se *). Enligt produktresum&eacute; effektduration upp till 24 timmar.</p>\r\n<p>*** Exakt duration och maxeffekt anges som ungef&auml;rliga d&aring; de varierar i olika studier. I klinisk praxis &auml;r det ingen skillnad mellan de olika l&auml;kemedlen.</p>\r\n<p># Insulin aspart med tillsats av nikotinamid: Fiasp godk&auml;ndes i hela EU januari 2017. J&auml;mf&ouml;rande studier med vanligt aspartinsulin (NovoRapid) visar n&aring;got snabbare tid till maxeffekt och kortare effektduration f&ouml;r Fiasp. Betydelsen av detta i klinisk praxis &auml;r &auml;nnu oklar.</p>"
